# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- Role-based access control for Admin, Interviewer, and Interviewee
- Modern UI components using Radix UI
- TypeScript type definitions
- Supabase integration for database and authentication
- File upload support for resumes and documents

### Changed
- Updated project structure to follow modern React patterns
- Improved routing system with role-based navigation
- Enhanced error handling and user feedback

### Removed
- CSV-based storage system
- Basic Flask backend

### Fixed
- CORS configuration
- Environment variable handling
- Routing issues

## [1.0.0] - 2025-03-23

### Added
- Initial project setup
- Basic routing structure
- Landing page
- Admin dashboard
- Interviewer dashboard
- Interviewee dashboard
- Interview management pages
- User management pages
- Feedback submission pages

### Changed
- Updated dependencies to latest versions
- Improved build configuration
- Enhanced development experience

### Removed
- Placeholder components
- Basic styling

### Fixed
- Initial setup issues
- Basic routing bugs

